CLIHelper, version 2.0

Changed signature for readInput()
    Switched argument order and now defaults to std::cin for input stream

Implemented argumentCount()
Implemented headIs()
Implemented argumentIs()
Implemented noArguments()
Implemented grabArgument()

Updated the example code

Changed the signature for fieldIs()
    Now takes strings instead of character arrays

Renamed extractField() -> grabField()

Changed the signature for grabField()
    Now returns a string instead of modifying a reference

Changed the signature for readInput()
    Now returns a string instead of modifying a reference

Updated README

Added changelog
